---
title: Sweet and Smoky Chipotle Double Chicken with Fresh Salad and Zesty Rice
description: Juicy sweet and sticky chicken breast slices adorn zesty lime rice in this Tex-Mex-inspired bowl. A fresh salad of spring mix and plump tomatoes adds veggie wholesomeness to an already delicious meal!
